Write a recursive CTE that walks the graph depth-first and returns every reachable dependency along with its minimum hop count. Use UNION (not UNION ALL) to avoid infinite loops if cycles exist.

Before publishing a breaking change to a low-level package, you need to know which packages depend on it — directly or transitively.

